{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act29side_level_act29side_03_end","storyGroup":"act29side","storySort":7,"storyDependence":"act29side_level_act29side_03_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"ZT-3","storyName":"练习曲“奇遇”","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"费德里科发现阿尔图罗可能正躲藏在学校。薇薇安娜在画家遗留的草稿上发现巫王残党的下一个目标可能是一位学者。同一时刻，这位学者打断了针对黑键的法术仪式。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act29side/level_act29side_03_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act29side_03","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":5,"next":7,"characters":["金律法卫","“巫王的余音”","薇薇安娜","珂拉","米夏","贵族侍从","费德里科","黑键","暴躁的老者","？？？","格哈德"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_storyendjp_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"彼得·卢卡斯男爵今年七十三岁。","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"三年前他从伯父那里继承了爵位。卢卡斯家祖传的高塔维修费用实在高昂，他不得不在半年后搬了家。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"他很喜欢卡尔·施密特的音乐，但很讨厌如今这条同名街道。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"阳光，花香，年轻人的涂鸦，还有不远处酒吧里传来的爵士乐都让他难以忍受。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"他让侍从拉上了窗帘，打开源石留声机。房间里立刻响起了大提琴声。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"那个萨科塔真的很有音乐天分，他想。他决定原谅她是个拉特兰人。","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"他自己会演奏十一种乐器，其中十种都是在巫王时代学会的。","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"为了把最好的旋律送进巫王的始源之塔，有天赋的年轻人被关在一起，没日没夜地创作。","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"他最爱其中的小提琴手，爱她纤细的手指和掌缘的痣。","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"当他第一次出访维多利亚，在皇家剧院的舞台上，听到一首又一首出自家乡的乐曲响起，他流下了眼泪，第一次亲吻了她。","id":18},{"type":"text","text":"这就是优雅、隽永的莱塔尼亚啊。","id":19},{"type":"text","text":"他真的很怀念它。","id":20},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":21},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_firemagic","id":22},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_wlfmster_01","flip":"1","layer":"1","id":23},{"type":"dialog","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":25},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"charslot","id":27},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":28},{"type":"bgeffect","id":29},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_bg_44_g1_marigold.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":30},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_suspenseful_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":32,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":33},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"3","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":34},{"type":"playsound","key":"$tactfulboost","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":36},{"type":"playsound","key":"$b_char_defboost","channel":"a","delay":"0.1","id":37},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":39},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_skill_rocksleep","channel":"b","delay":"0.2","id":40},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":41},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","duration":"0.5","id":42},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"......","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"故意摧毁民居，想借机逃出去？","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"在黄金旋律面前，你们的卑劣无处藏身。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":47},{"type":"charslot","id":48},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"2","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"2","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":49},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_swrdbzz","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":51},{"type":"charslot","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1128_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":54},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","action":"shake","power":"10","times":"50","duration":"0.3","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"呃——唔！","id":56},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"你是最后一个。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"摘下面具，向莱塔尼亚的意志投降。这样你就不必再忍受灵魂的灼痛。","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1128_1#1$1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"这份灼痛......太过微小。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"金律法卫阁下，您可曾听过属于巫王的皇家乐团的演奏？","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"恩瓦德的黑森林，福特冈的湖泊与港口，施彤领的风暴......您能想象到的关于莱塔尼亚的一切，都能在旋律中感受到。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"巫王并不演绎，也从不指挥。他只漫步于其中。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"作为他的乐手，你不得不依据他视线的指引，紧随着他的步伐前行。一旦掉队，你就会......被壮美的旋律撕裂。","id":65,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"这是巫王最常用的刑罚，用以惩处那些不配在他身边侍奉的弱者。","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1128_1#1$1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"但我跟上过。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"我成了那超越想象的旋律的一部分。在那之后，我已无法容忍再为任何庸人演奏。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"你们把自己当作什么？伟大旋律的演绎者，心怀理想的颠覆者？","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"不。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"我看到的只有一群躲藏在面具后面，戕害无辜莱塔尼亚人性命、破坏和谐秩序的罪人......以及无能的、将头埋在巫王余烬中的小丑。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"黄金旋律会取走你们的性命。","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"但是，在放弃自我、成为巫王附庸的那一刻，你们就已经与死人无异。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"charslot","id":78},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gldswrdclave","id":79},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1128_1#1$1","id":81},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"呃啊......哈......哈哈！","id":84,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"那您呢，阁下？别忘了，您也戴着面具。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"您使用的源石技艺，这被一代又一代金律法卫传承下来的法术——黄金旋律，莱塔尼亚的辉光，守卫金律乐章的力量——","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"不也是......某段出自更伟大的意志之手的，旋律的附庸？","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"再伟大的个体意志，都无法与莱塔尼亚本身相提并论。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1128_1#1$1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"那此时此刻......宣判我的死亡的......","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"究竟是莱塔尼亚的黄金旋律，还是您自己？","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"这是你找的后路吗？难道你认为，这些苍白的旧调，当真能撼动金律法卫的意志？","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"荒谬。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1128_1#1$1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"为什么......要找后路？","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"我本就是......被选中过来见您的。","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"“首席”想让我问问您......就在刚才，二十三年前的往事在您耳畔奏响......","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"您看到......身受致命伤，却等不到您支援的恩斯特·霍赫贝格......","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“巫王的余音”","text":"还有他那被迫当上选帝侯，郁郁而终的弟弟沃尔纳了吗？","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_1128_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"......","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":104},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.3","id":105},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":106},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gldswrdclave","id":107},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_smkedspte","id":110},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":111},{"type":"text","text":"巫王残党的身躯在双重源石技艺的作用下崩解成飞灰。","id":112},{"type":"text","text":"和最后一缕烟尘一起扑向金律法卫的，还有她喑哑的遗言。","id":113},{"type":"dialog","id":114},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"subtitle","text":"布兰特·赖纳。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":116},{"type":"subtitle","text":"你不可能永远逃避选择。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":117},{"type":"subtitle","id":118},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":119},{"type":"dialog","id":120},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":121},{"type":"charslot","id":122},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":123},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":124},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","id":125},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","id":126},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_wasteland_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":128,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"二十三年前，父亲没有等到母亲。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"他们彼此错过了。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"那天上午，露辛达来到画室之前，先去了香料市场。她好几天没什么精神，想换种香薰提提神。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"那时候她还不知道，自己和爱人有了一个孩子。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"......","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"后来，母亲还是去了施彤领。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"她很爱你，也爱沃尔纳。而且，留在崔林特尔梅的话，她一个人照顾不了你。","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"她知道那时候的沃尔纳已另娶他人，可她别无选择。","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"但父亲原本还有机会。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"十分钟。要是沃尔纳再多停留十分钟，他就能见到露辛达。他会得知，她愿意同他一起面对，一起抗争。","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"这十分钟......成了沃尔纳一生的遗憾。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/eb/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"......我明白。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"父亲从未对我提起过，但我都明白。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"金盏花，和月亮......本就没有关联。这只是一个梦，一个醒着的人聊以安慰自己的、遥不可及的理想。","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"你......不怪你父亲吗？","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"我不能。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"因为我和他，是那般相像。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"你们都告诉我，父亲曾经梦想成为一名诗人。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"但他从未在我面前念过一首诗歌。","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"回到莱塔尼亚之后......我才理解。当一个人已无力面对现实时，那些曾带来过希望的意象，都会反过来刺痛他。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"......薇薇安娜。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"你父亲走后，从施彤领到崔林特尔梅，你一直在忙碌。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"我想让你知道......你是可以表现出悲伤的。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"......","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"我想再休息一会。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"一会就好。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d5/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":167},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","text":"","id":168},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":169},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":170},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_pullcurtain","volume":"0.7","text":"","id":171},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":173},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","volume":"0.7","text":"","id":174},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":175},{"type":"text","text":"珂拉没有再说什么。在离去之前，她拉上了窗帘。","id":176},{"type":"text","text":"黑暗如同一床熟悉的被子，包裹住了薇薇安娜。珂拉是那样了解她，知道什么环境最让她感到安心。","id":177},{"type":"text","text":"她注视着房间里一幅又一幅掩埋在阴影中的画，画中本该金灿灿的时光也注视着她。","id":178},{"type":"dialog","id":179},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"charslot","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":182},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f7/Avg_bg_44_g5_spiralstairs.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":183},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":186},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":188},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"幸好，琴声中的源石技艺没有对薇薇安娜造成什么实质伤害。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"但她和我们一样，想起了与沃尔纳相关的往事。她一定比我们更不好受。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"你受伤了。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"是吗？","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"啊......不是战斗导致的。可能是在下楼追赶薇薇安娜的时候，撞伤了吧。","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"为什么不试一下我从哥伦比亚带回来的康复仪？","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"布兰特，我的眼睛不是昨天才刚受伤的。这二十多年跌跌撞撞的，不也一样过来了吗？","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"倒是你......声音有些奇怪。刚刚那些敌人，很难对付？","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"可能吗？","id":204,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"这语气才更像你。","id":206,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"不过，你呀......真希望你偶尔也能摘下头盔，喘口气。就算是最厉害的乐器，一直持续不断地投入使用的话，也会有损耗的。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"我没有休息的资格。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"宪兵队正在赶来这里的路上。他们会处理现场，帮助伤亡的民众。","id":210,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"在他们封锁街道之前，尽快离开。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"现在吗？可我们正在接近真相。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"一个视力受损的调音师，一个退役的竞技骑士......莱塔尼亚的未来还不至于要托付到你们手里。","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"残党们正在寻找巫王的遗产。弗里达和洛里斯都是那一夜的目击者。沃尔纳......霍赫贝格家族也参与了那场政变。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"假如他们想通过杀死目击者来完成某种仪式的话，他们一定会去寻找下一个目标。","id":218,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"所以，听我的话，停止调查。","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"......","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/44/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"那你呢，布兰特？要说政变当天也在现场的话，你明明也......","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"我是莱塔尼亚意志的捍卫者。巫王残党还奈何不了我。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"更何况，他们在这条巷子里设下埋伏，显然已将你们视作目标。","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"他们为何觉得我们一定会来？难道薇薇安娜的猜测是真的，弗里达的画里还藏着至关重要的线索？","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":230},{"type":"charslot","id":231},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":232},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"恐怕是的。","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"布兰特阁下，请允许我继续调查。我想，我知道希曼夫人留下了什么。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"你手里的是......弗里达最后一幅作品的草稿。","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"“遗憾”。","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"这是画家这一生最强烈的情感，也是最深的渴望。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"在生命的最后，她一遍又一遍地画着这幅画。","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"只是因为，她想通过自己的画笔，再一次见到心中的神明。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/85/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"这些乱糟糟的笔触并非随机涂抹？","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"嗯。画面看起来凌乱，是因为她在同一张纸上画了太多遍。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"巫王死去时的那一幕，依然藏在草稿之中。","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"薇薇安娜，把画放在地上。","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"好的。","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_4098_vvana_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1113_1#1$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"布兰特，试着“演奏”画幅。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_1113_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1117_1#2$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"你说停的时候，我会停下。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1117_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":256},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"bg","duration":"3","from":"0","to":"1","block":"false","id":258},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_swrdbzz","id":259},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"2","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":260},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"画幅在振动，就像乐器一样。","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"......嗯。","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"每一遍绘制，弗里达使用的颜料都有细微的差别。","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"我看不见，但我的源石技艺，能够让我“听”到每一层颜料的频率。","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"快了......只要剥离上层的源石颜料，就能找到......","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"最初的画面。","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"你们看见了吗？","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"不是很清楚，但能看到高塔内部。很......壮观。","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"......巫王塔。我想，就算是弗里达，也只能画出很小的一部分。","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"珂拉","text":"能不能辨认画上的人？","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"没有巫王。王座面前是空着的，战斗似乎已经结束。","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"躲在帷幔后面的，是弗里达·希曼，画家自己。","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"有士兵正从外面走廊上冲进来，那是一个黎博利......洛里斯·博尔丁？","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"还有......唔......","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"这个正在清理残骸的，拿着施术单元的卡普里尼是谁？","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"格哈德·霍夫曼。","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"他是整个恩瓦德最具天赋的术师之一，曾经服务于乌提卡家族。","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"金律法卫","text":"在巫王死后，他成了一名老师。","id":279},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialog","id":281},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":282},{"type":"charslot","id":283},{"type":"bg","duration":"0","from":"1","to":"0","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":285},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/08/Avg_bg_44_g1_marigold.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":286},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":287},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":289,"musicid":3},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":290},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":291},{"type":"delay","time":"1.2","id":292},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"我们来晚了。","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ea/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"这帮亡命之徒，压根不在意普通人的性命......真的该死。","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ea/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"charslot","id":297},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"10","vibrato":"5","randomness":"50","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":298},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","posfrom":"0,-50","posto":"0,0","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贵族侍从","text":"咳咳......咳咳咳。","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":302},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你受伤了。请让我帮你止血。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贵族侍从","text":"谢谢。","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"楼上就是卢卡斯男爵的住处。他情况怎么样？","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贵族侍从","text":"男爵他......没能逃掉。","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贵族侍从","text":"唉，他早就想搬家了。要不是最近总能听到一个萨科塔在附近拉琴，他开始舍不得走，我们又怎么会赶上这些倒霉事哟！","id":311,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"那是什么样的琴声？","id":313,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贵族侍从","text":"你要听吗？男爵都让我录下来了，也不知道留声机有没有被那帮人弄坏......","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.3","fadetime":"2","id":316},{"type":"dialog","id":317},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":318},{"type":"charslot","id":319},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","id":320},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1","id":321},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":323},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"你还真找到了线索。","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"是洛里斯·博尔丁找到的。","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":330},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":331},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cello_1","id":332},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":333},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":334},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"是阿尔图罗的演奏吗？","id":338,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"没错。","id":340,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我的确听不出一段相同的旋律是出自人还是雕塑，可我不可能错认阿尔图罗的琴声。","id":341,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"那我们岂不是身处危险之中？！","id":343,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f1/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不必担心，录音中并没有源石技艺。她也不在附近。几分钟之前，有人在这条街道上同步播送了她的琴声。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"她的源石技艺生效范围......这么大？","id":347,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"她一定有同伴在身侧。只有你们莱塔尼亚人的法术和她的源石技艺共同作用，才可能有这种效果。","id":349,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"你能听出这么多信息？","id":351,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这里。这段声响不是大提琴能发出来的。这是管风琴，而且大小超乎寻常。","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"巨型管风琴......","id":355,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/20/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"听起来很独特。崔林特尔梅附近哪里有类似乐器？","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/bc/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"......路德维格大学。","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/98/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"一所学校？","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4109_baslin_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"米夏","text":"嗯。那里原本是......乌提卡家族世代求学的高塔。","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/20/Avg_avg_4109_baslin_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":364},{"type":"dialog","id":365},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":366},{"type":"charslot","id":367},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":368},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":371},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":373},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_tinnitus","volume":"1","id":374},{"type":"delay","time":"0.01","id":375},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.3","id":376},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"......","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":379},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":380},{"type":"text","text":"头痛。","id":381},{"type":"text","text":"在逃离维谢海姆之后，他几乎没有再经历过如此剧烈的疼痛。","id":382},{"type":"text","text":"上一次疼得想要大喊大叫，想要呕吐，想要泪流满面......还是什么时候？","id":383},{"type":"text","text":"是......","id":384},{"type":"text","text":"他记得的。他只是不愿意回忆。","id":385},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.3","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"为什么......不开口说话？","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"你可以嘲笑我了。我把你在脑子里关了这么久，你终于要赢了。","id":388,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"等我死了以后......哈，我最好真能干脆地死掉。","id":389,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"像你这样，明明死了这么长时间，连尸骨都化了灰，还要被忠诚的仆人从碎片拼回来，拉回尘世......也太可笑了。","id":390,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":391},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":392},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d0/Avg_bg_44_g4_towerroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":393},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#5$1","id":394},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_ponder_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":395,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"他在胡言乱语些什么？","id":397,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"格哈德，你的术式还没启动吧？","id":398,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":399},{"type":"charslot","id":400},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"没有，老师。","id":402,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"他看起来非常难受。他真的能熬过去吗？","id":403,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#10$1","id":404},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"啧，再怎么说也是赫尔昏佐伦的血脉。这点苦都吃不下去，伊维格娜德是故意让人把他养成了废物吧。","id":405,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"他还很年轻，却已经吃了很多苦。","id":407,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"如果他承受不了术式，尘世之音的演奏中断，“始源之角”的降临可能会失控，整个路德维格都会受影响。","id":408,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#12$1","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"有我在，高塔塌不了。","id":410,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"可是您答应过陛下，不能暴露您的力量。让那么多的学生得知您的身份，陛下就不得不对其他贵族有所交代。","id":412,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"到时候，路德维格大学可能会被迫关停，您接下来的搬迁计划也会有阻碍。","id":413,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"等小埃米送完信回到莱塔尼亚，一定会念叨您的。","id":414,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#5$1","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"......麻烦。要保这小子的命，真比唤回“始源之角”还难。","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#2$1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"莱辛呢？","id":418,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"他去外面守着了。","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"莱辛说，他会确保在仪式结束前，他们进不来。","id":421,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$1","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"算了，不就是要保住他的意识不被扯碎吗？上回我给玻利瓦尔那伙疯子做的法术装置去哪了......","id":423,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/a0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":424},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":425},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":426},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":427},{"type":"charslot","id":428},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"......","id":430,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你还好吗？","id":432,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"呵......","id":434,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","bstart":"0.15","bend":"0.5","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"没事的。他们都暂时离开了。","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"你......是......","id":438,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":439},{"type":"charslot","id":440},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":441},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":442},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"我们不久前刚见过面。","id":443,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$1","id":444},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"密林......公园......","id":445,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"是的。我本想提醒你，但莱辛也在。有他盯着，我没法带你走。","id":447,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","id":448},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"莱辛......","id":449,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#5$1","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"那孩子本性不坏，就是有些认死理。","id":451,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3d/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"我以前也和他一样......可人只要有勇气，就能有所改变。","id":452,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3d/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$1","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"......嗯。","id":454,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1f/Avg_avg_4046_ebnhlz_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#1$1","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"你还有力气吗？试试看，握紧我的手。","id":456,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":457},{"type":"charslot","id":458},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#7$1","duration":"0.5","id":459},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":460},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"格哈德，你在做什么？！","id":462,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#3$1","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"抱歉，老师。","id":464,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"我不能让您这样利用赫尔昏佐伦的血脉。他是个活生生的人，还能拥有辉煌的未来。","id":465,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":466},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.15","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":467},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#3$1","id":468},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spelldfns_2","id":469},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":470},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#12$1","id":471},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"空间防御术式——该死，这还是我教你的！","id":472,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#3$1","id":473},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"再强大的源石技艺都无法弥补遗憾......这也是您教我的。","id":474,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"我曾经用您教我的法术，伤害过很多人。","id":475,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"在午夜梦回的时刻，我常常责问自己——假如当初我没有那么做，那些本可以继续闪耀的灵魂就不会在我手中消逝。","id":476,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"那我们如今所处的这个时代，身边的人，包括我们自身......是不是会变得更好？","id":477,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"所以我才放弃了高塔术师的身份，成为一名学者。","id":478,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6b/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#7$1","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"格哈德，你在说什么胡话？","id":480,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"暴躁的老者","text":"把那小子留下，不要犯错——","id":481,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#5$1","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"......犯错？","id":483,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3d/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1124_1#8$1","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"不，老师。","id":485,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格哈德","text":"我要救他，正是因为，我不能再错过这个机会。我要挽回我和您......我们犯过的最大的错。","id":486,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_1124_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"backgroundtween","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":487},{"type":"dialog","id":488},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","id":489},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spelldfns_2","id":490},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":491},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":492},{"type":"dialog","id":493},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":494},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":495},{"type":"image","id":496},{"type":"charslot","id":497}],"characters":["金律法卫","“巫王的余音”","薇薇安娜","珂拉","米夏","贵族侍从","费德里科","黑键","暴躁的老者","？？？","格哈德"]}